{"tid":1001771,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"「低語者」領袖之女遭囚禁！《陰屍路》第九季釋季中回歸新預告","createTime":"2019-01-30T11:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T15:58:51.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8916066bb7faad31e84e794d71e7b0ec76385d0c","tid":1001771,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:51:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mTPeic9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmTPeic9.jpg&h=68ccacb6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAMC 美劇《陰屍路》（The Walking Dead）發布第九季下半季預告，反派「低語者」（The Whisperers）領導阿爾法（Alpha）的女兒首度登場。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n此支預告以米瓊（Michonne，戴娜葛里拉 飾）牽著一隻載有蒙眼囚犯的馬開場，後看到這名囚犯實為阿爾法的女兒莉迪亞（Lydia），由《親愛的初戀》女星凱莎蒂麥琳西（Cassady McClincy）飾演。她在上半季混亂的局勢中，被戴瑞（Daryl，諾曼李杜斯 飾）和米瓊找到，扯下屍皮面具的她露出真面目，後被關在牢籠中。而她的「低語者」同伴們緊接著在預告後段現身，準備和倖存者們展開對戰。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n▼《陰屍路》第九季下半季預告。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/k65ikZmyT_4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fk65ikZmyT_4&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=f1554a09\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/k65ikZmyT_4</a><br />\n「低語者」被描述成穿著屍皮、戴著面具，低調行走如活屍的一個團體。領導者阿爾法性格狡猾又冷酷，由《怪獸與牠們的產地》英國女星珊曼莎摩頓（Samantha Morton）飾演，其副手貝塔（Beta）則是名殘暴的傢伙，對任何外人有很強的攻擊性，由《飆風不歸路》男星雷恩赫斯（Ryan Hurst）演出。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n第九季下半季回歸首集將接續上季結尾，描述戴瑞（Daryl，諾曼李杜斯 飾）一行人帶著耶穌（Jesus，湯姆佩恩 飾）的屍體返回山頂寨。而逃跑的尼根（Negan，傑佛利迪恩摩根 飾）則拿回了心愛的露西爾，吹著令人毛骨悚然的旋律，似乎打算東山再起。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n《陰屍路》第九季下半季將於美國時間 2 月 10 日回歸。台灣 FOX 頻道與影音串流平台 FOX+ 於 2 月 11 日起，每周一與美同步播出。（ew）"},{"pid":"a438eb85d87b910944521c8c33d917993d16d962","tid":1001771,"uid":212399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcdd02bd2c2bd8f9e2787713684d726c9bdefa6","tid":1001771,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T11:56:01.000Z","msg":"仆街啦,又畀Negan走甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我估實將佢洗白跟手寫死埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"badea285d358c8a391cbd556624c90207f2e4658","tid":1001771,"uid":35014,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:00:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"db8db1747a5858e9370df354fb41eaf832a0429f","tid":1001771,"uid":34436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"自從carl自己on99咁俾屍咬到已經放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRick全家含包散都唔知有咩好睇 <br />\n<br />\nbtw season 1 啲人死晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d6acad932e523a44a03b6437f8910f47c71b5f","tid":1001771,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db8db1747a5858e9370df354fb41eaf832a0429f","tid":1001771,"uid":34436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"自從carl自己on99咁俾屍咬到已經放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRick全家含包散都唔知有咩好睇 <br />\n<br />\nbtw season 1 啲人死晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"未,仲有弓佬同呀婆"},{"pid":"ffb620375db47a13809e4398821c95c6025e8bad","tid":1001771,"uid":111497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90d6acad932e523a44a03b6437f8910f47c71b5f","tid":1001771,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"db8db1747a5858e9370df354fb41eaf832a0429f","tid":1001771,"uid":34436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:05:28.000Z","msg":"自從carl自己on99咁俾屍咬到已經放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nRick全家含包散都唔知有咩好睇 <br />\n<br />\nbtw season 1 啲人死晒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:07:46.000Z","msg":"未,仲有弓佬同呀婆"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T12:09:17.000Z","msg":"弓佬好似係原創角?阿婆好似漫畫一早死9左?"},{"